episodes.name: Trying to Get to Heaven Before They Close the Door
episodes.overview: Rue and Jules cross paths for the first time since Christmas as East Highland rings in the new year.

episodes.name: Out of Touch
episodes.overview: As the semester kicks off, Jules questions Rue and Elliot's new friendship. While Cal hunts for answers, Nate makes a tough decision. The lines between fantasy and reality begin to blur as Kat ponders her relationship, and Maddy contemplates the decision to end hers.

episodes.name: Ruminations: Big and Little Bullys
episodes.overview: Rue pursues a new business venture, Cassie settles into a routine, and Cal finds a target.

episodes.name: You Who Cannot See, Think of Those Who Can
episodes.overview: At Maddy’s birthday party, relationships are celebrated and questioned. Meanwhile, Jules turns to Elliot for advice and Cal takes a trip down memory lane.

episodes.name: Stand Still Like the Hummingbird
episodes.overview: Fate has a way of catching up with those who try to outrun it.

episodes.name: A Thousand Little Trees of Blood
episodes.overview: As relationships with mothers are tested, Rue tries to recover. Meanwhile, Lexi questions the possible backlash from her play, and Nate celebrates his newfound freedom.

episodes.name: The Theater and Its Double
episodes.overview: Art imitates life as the East Highland crew watches their complicated dynamics reflected in Lexi's long-awaited play. Meanwhile, Fezco gets ready to attend.

episodes.name: All My Life, My Heart Has Yearned for a Thing I Cannot Name
episodes.overview: As the show goes on, fragments of memories collide with the present and future.
